Requirements:
Falsk and Sqlite3 are required for running this application.
$ sudo pip install Flask
$ sudo apt-get install sqlite3

Step1: create the sqlite db
    Run the command 'sqlite3 /tmp/flaskr.db < schema.sql' before run this application for create the db.
Step2: Run the app 
  dennis@ubuntu14:~/flaskr$ python flaskr.py 
 * Running on http://0.0.0.0:5000/ (Press CTRL+C to quit)
 * Restarting with stat
Step3: Test it
    Browsing http://localhost:5000, or via IP. eg: http://192.168.237.128:5000
    
Note: This application is from http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/0.10/tutorial/.
